        "comment": "The new snow and wind slabs of the last few days are poorly bonded with the old snowpack above the tree line. <br/> Distinct weak layers exist in the old snowpack. This applies especially on west, north and east facing slopes. <br/> Night: Over a wide area 5 cm of snow, and even more in some localities, has fallen above approximately 1200 m."
